addLiquidity(address).notice: Allows users to add liquidity to the pool in exchange for LP tokens. Taxed tokens are not supported. The recipient will receive the minted LP tokens.

recoverTokens(address,address).notice: Recovers tokens mistakenly sent to the Pool contract and sends them to the specified recipient.

redeemLiquidity(address).notice: Allows users to redeem their LP tokens for underlying assets. The recipient will receive the redeemed tokens.

skim(address,address).notice: Allows the caller to transfer excess thisToken or thatToken to a specified recipient. The recipient will receive the excess tokens.

swap(address).notice: Allows users to swap tokens in the pool. The recipient will receive the swapped tokens.
